.TITLE Graphs - mermaid

```mermaid
graph LR;
   subgraph K8s
        API
    end

   subgraph ControllerSG[Ingress Controller]
        K8sInformers

        subgraph LoopSG[Event Loop]

                Event{Event}
                Event --> K8sEV[k8s event]
                K8sEV --> Storage[Storage + Runtime]
                Storage --> Loop
                Event --> Command
                Command --> Config[Update configuration]
                Config --> Loop
                Loop --> Event
        end
   end

   API --> K8sInformers
   K8sInformers --> Event
```

